As of April 1, 2018, Nova Scotia Regional School Boards became Regional Centres for Education (RCE). Geographical areas for regional centres and their historical school boards can be found here: https://novascotia.ca/just/regulations/regs/edregcen.htm . The Conseil scolaire acadien provincial (CSAP) remained the same.
